    • Method Detail

      • mayAlias

        public AccessPath mayAlias(AccessPath taintedAP,
                           AccessPath referencedAP)
        Gets whether an access path can point to the same runtime object as another or to an object reachable through the other
        Parameters:
        taintedAP - The access path that is tainted
        referencedAP - The access path that is accessed
        Returns:
        The access path that actually matched if the access paths alias. In the simplest case, this is the given tainted access path. When using recursive access paths, it can however also be a base expansion. If the given access paths do not alias, null is returned.

      • getReferencedAPBase

        private AccessPath getReferencedAPBase(AccessPath taintedAP,
                                       soot.SootField[] referencedFields)
        Matches the given access path against the given array of fields
        Parameters:
        taintedAP - The tainted access paths
        referencedFields - The array of referenced access paths
        Returns:
        The actually matched access path if a matching was possible, otherwise null

      • mayAlias

        public boolean mayAlias(soot.Value val1,
                        soot.Value val2)
        Gets whether two values may potentially point to the same runtime object
        Parameters:
        val1 - The first value
        val2 - The second value
        Returns:

      • mayAlias

        public AccessPath mayAlias(AccessPath ap,
                           soot.Value val)
        Gets whether a value and an access path may potentially point to the same runtime object
        Parameters:
        ap - The access path
        val - The value
        Returns:
        The access path that actually matched if the given value and access path alias. In the simplest case, this is the given access path. When using recursive access paths, it can however also be a base expansion. If the given access path and value do not alias, null is returned.

      • mustAlias

        Gets whether the two fields must always point to the same runtime object
        Parameters:
        field1 - The first field
        field2 - The second field
        Returns:
        True if the two fields must always point to the same runtime object, otherwise false

        Gets whether the two values must always point to the same runtime object
